{"tid":950148,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［玩撚完］比利：麥巴比係新比利","createTime":"2018-12-21T09:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T10:34:57.000Z","uid":4661,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8ba118f94012b94dc77efc10c3d3e76c6ef424","tid":950148,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181221/s00006/1f7337d2ce7691f58a57ff515ff88ac1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181221%2Fs00006%2F1f7337d2ce7691f58a57ff515ff88ac1.jpg&h=975541c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181221/s00006/1f122aa8ddd00b938f4fa767ebd9397a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181221%2Fs00006%2F1f122aa8ddd00b938f4fa767ebd9397a.jpg&h=06c12392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國新星基利安麥巴比昨日步入20歲，獲得不少恭賀，當中包括已78歲的巴西球王比利。後者認為麥巴比今夏能贏得世界盃，他日成就能媲美自己。<br />\n<br />\n比利60年前協助巴西贏得1958年世界盃，當年他只有17歲，而麥巴比今夏也不足20歲稱雄世盃，比利在網上發帖稱：「只有奇才這麼早表現到自己。生日快樂，基利安。20歲的時光，我對未來的憧憬感到興奮。」他早幾日接受法國傳媒訪問時說「麥巴比會是新比利，巴黎聖日耳門打出水準應可晉身歐聯決賽。」比利又在網上談到35年前雷米金盃被盜一事，笑說自己至少在失竊前，曾與獎盃共度美好時光。"},{"pid":"921fdac77308f4808d3375ba9062d217cdcb0ccb","tid":950148,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"包皮RIP"},{"pid":"69cb0493f4c86557b51a291077d01192a3e09618","tid":950148,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892c8eb10b182d33dcb03f020adc50a511e598e7","tid":950148,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef3261134650bc585e47ee61c812522dc7dfe75","tid":950148,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"好彩牠拿了世界盃<img src=\"/assets/